_sText:
Hello everyone, windowstopuser here! And this is my first ever map of CS:Source, and it took me 2-3 hours to make in Hammer. It's a snowy deathmatch map with sniper spots, snow covers and even a "secret" area!

- Includes bot support up to ~19 bots! (Warning: may reduce the performance of your PC)
